# Discovering OpenSees -- Basic Reliability Analysis using OpenSees

This seminar will occur March 27 at 2 p.m. (Pacific Time) and will be conducted by Prof. Michael Scott, Oregon State University

Register for the seminar:

  • March 27, 2:00 pm Pacific Time registration 1

This seminar will discuss how to perform basic reliability analysis using OpenSees.

The following topics will be discussed:

  • What is "Reliability Analysis"
  • How is it Done Using OpenSees
  • Summary and conclusions
